  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      An ecologically friendly and biodegradable wood-plastic composite-cast is studied. Patients,
      who has sustained a distal radius fracture in need of splinting are requested to participate
      in the study.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
