  <primary_outcome>
    <measure>How well will the material fulfil the demands of a splinting material</measure>
    <time_frame>1 year</time_frame>
    <description>The aim of the study was to evaluate how well the material fulfils the demands of a splinting material, the subjective satisfaction of the treatment and the orthopaedic technicians´opinion of the material.The following parameters will be detected: immobilisation-time, conservative / operative treatment, re-reposition, mechanical properties of the cast, skin appearance or irritation caused by the cast, allergic reactions and subjective opinion.</description>
  </primary_outcome>
